{"kanda":6,"sarga":125,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"उपस्थितंतुतंकृत्वापुष्पकंपुष्पभूषितम् ।अविदूरेस्थितोराममित्युवाचविभीषणः","trans":"Offering to Sri Rama the Pushpak decorated with flowers to sit, Vibheeshana stood at a distance and spoke.","words":[{"d":"पुष्पभूषितम्","m":"decorated with flowers"},{"d":"तम्","m":"that"},{"d":"पुष्पकम्","m":"Pushpaka"},{"d":"उपस्थितम्","m":"seated"},{"d":"कृत्वा","m":"having"},{"d":"अविदूरे","m":"little distance"},{"d":"स्थितः","m":"stood"},{"d":"रामम्","m":"Rama"},{"d":"इति","m":"this"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"स तुबद्धाञ्जलि: प्रह्वोविनीतोराक्षसेश्वरः ।अब्रवीत्त्वरयोपेतःकिंकरोमीतिराघवम्","trans":"The Rakshasa king humbly offered salutation to Raghava with joined palms, quickly approached, and said, 'What is to be done'?","words":[{"d":"सःराक्षसेश्वरः","m":"he, Rakshasa king"},{"d":"विनीतः","m":"humbly"},{"d":"बद्धाञ्जलिप्रह्व:","m":"saluting with folded palms"},{"d":"त्वरया","m":"quickly"},{"d":"उपेतः","m":"approached"},{"d":"किम्","m":"why"},{"d":"करोमि","m":"to be done"},{"d":"इति","m":"this"},{"d":"राघवम्","m":"to Raghava"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"तमब्रवीन्महातेजालक्ष्मणस्योपशृण्वतः ।विमृश्यराघवोवाक्यमिदंस्नेहपुरस्कृतम्","trans":"Highly brilliant Raghava was thinking and spoke in a friendly manner while Lakshmana was listening closely.","words":[{"d":"महातेजाः","m":"highly brilliant"},{"d":"राघवः","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"विमृश्य","m":"thinking"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणस्य","m":"Lakshmana's"},{"d":"उपशृण्वतः","m":"while listening closely"},{"d":"तम्","m":"him"},{"d":"स्नेहपुरस्कृतम्","m":"in friendly manner"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"this"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"कृतप्रयत्नकर्माणःसर्वएववनेचराः ।रत्नैरर्थैश्चविविधैस्सम्पूज्यन्तांविभीषण","trans":"\"Let all the forest rangers (without exception) who made effort and fought be duly honoured with valuables and several luxuries.\"","words":[{"d":"विभीषण","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"कृतप्रयत्नकर्माणः","m":"who fought making effort"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"वनेचराः","m":"forest rangers"},{"d":"रत्नैः","m":"with valuables"},{"d":"विविधैः","m":"several"},{"d":"अर्थैश्च","m":"and luxuries"},{"d":"सम्पूज्यन्ताम्","m":"duly honoured"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"सहामीभिस्त्वयालङ्कानिर्जिताराक्षसेश्वर ।हृष्टैःप्राणभयंत्यक्त्वासङ्ग्रामेष्वनिवर्तिभिः","trans":"\"This Lanka could be won with the help of these heroes who never turned back and fought in comb at without fear of life, O Lord of Rakshasas.\"","words":[{"d":"राक्षसेश्वर","m":"Rakshasa Lord"},{"d":"हृष्टैः","m":"delighted"},{"d":"प्राणभयम्","m":"fear of life"},{"d":"त्यक्त्वा","m":"giving up"},{"d":"सङ्ग्रामेषु","m":"in the combat"},{"d":"अनिवर्तिभिः","m":"who never turned back"},{"d":"अमीभिःसह","m":"with these heroes"},{"d":"त्वया","m":"by you"},{"d":"लङ्का","m":"Lanka"},{"d":"निर्जिता","m":"could win"}]},{"v":6,"dev":"त इमेकृतकर्माणस्सर्वएववनौकसः ।धनरत्नप्रदानेनकर्मैषांसफलंकुरु","trans":"\"These forest rangers, all of them have struggled and accomplished success. Reward them with wealth and gems.\"","words":[{"d":"ते","m":"you"},{"d":"इमे","m":"these"},{"d":"वनौकसः","m":"forest rangers"},{"d":"सर्वेएव","m":"all in that way"},{"d":"कृतकर्माणः","m":"accomplishment"},{"d":"धनरत्नप्रदानेन","m":"wealth and gems"},{"d":"एषाम्","m":"such effort"},{"d":"कर्म","m":"deed"},{"d":"सफलम्","m":"successful"},{"d":"कुरु","m":"make it"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"एवंसम्मानिताश्चेतेमानार्हमानदात्वया ।भविष्यन्तिकृतज्ञेननिर्वृताहरियूथपाः","trans":"\"These helpless monkey troops will be content with gratitude when rewarded, O respectable Vibheeshana.\"","words":[{"d":"आनदा","m":"helpless"},{"d":"मानार्हम्","m":"who respects"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"that way"},{"d":"कृतज्ञेन","m":"in gratitude"},{"d":"त्वया","m":"you"},{"d":"सम्मानिताः","m":"reward"},{"d":"एते","m":"these"},{"d":"हरियूथपाः","m":"monkey troops निर्वृता contended"},{"d":"भविष्यन्ति","m":"will be"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"त्यागिनंसङ्ग्रहीतारंसानुक्रोशंजितेन्द्रियम् ।सर्वेततःअवगच्छन्तिसम्बोधयामिते","trans":"\"If you do so you will be called as charitable and kind, not seizing wealth and as one who has gained over senses. That is why I am telling you for so long.\"","words":[{"d":"त्यागिनम्","m":"charitable"},{"d":"सङ्ग्रहीतारम्","m":"not seizing"},{"d":"सानुक्रोशम्","m":"compassionate"},{"d":"जितेन्द्रियम्","m":"gained over senses"},{"d":"त्वाम्","m":"you"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"अवगच्छन्ति","m":"telling you for so long"},{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"ते","m":"you"},{"d":"सम्बोधयामि","m":"will call you"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"हीनंरतिगुणैस्सर्वैरभिहन्तारमाहवे ।सेनात्यजतिसम्विग्नानृपतिंतंनरेश्वरा","trans":"\"O Ruler of men, all the army will desert a king who is devoid of virtues, lowly and who is a destructor in the battlefield.\"","words":[{"d":"नरेश्वरा","m":"ruler of men"},{"d":"सर्वैः","m":"all"},{"d":"रतिगुणैः","m":"devoid of virtues"},{"d":"हीनम्","m":"low"},{"d":"आहवे","m":"in battle"},{"d":"हन्तारम्","m":"destructor"},{"d":"तंनृपतिम्","m":"that king"},{"d":"सेना","m":"army"},{"d":"त्यजति","m":"will desert"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"एवमुक्तस्तुरामेणवानरांस्तान्विभीषणः ।रत्नार्थसंविभागेनसर्वानेवाभ्यपूजयत्","trans":"Vibheeshana honoured the Vanaras with gems and valuables, after Rama had spoken like that.","words":[{"d":"रामेण","m":"by Rama"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"उक्तः","m":"spoken"},{"d":"विभीषणः","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"सर्वानेव","m":"all"},{"d":"तान् वानरान्","m":"those Vanaras"},{"d":"रत्नार्थसम्विभागेन","m":"with gems, gold and valuables"},{"d":"अभ्यपूजयत्","m":"honoured them very much"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"ततस्तान्पूजितान्दृष्टवारत्नार्थैर्हरियूथपान् ।आरुरोहतदारामस्तद्विमानमनुत्तमम्","trans":"Then on seeing the monkey troops being honoured with excellent gemsRama ascended the aerial car.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"रत्नार्थैः","m":"with gems"},{"d":"तान् हरियूथपान्","m":"those monkey troops"},{"d":"पूजितान्","m":"offered prayers"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"अनुत्तमम्","m":"excellent"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"विमानम्","m":"aerial car"},{"d":"आरुरोह","m":"ascended"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"अङ्केनादायवैदेहींलज्जमानांयशस्विनीम् ।लक्ष्मणेनसहभ्रात्राविक्रान्तेवधनुष्मता","trans":"Illustrious Sita who was feeling shy, seeing the monkeys and valiant archer Lakshmana took Sita in his arms to Pushpaka.","words":[{"d":"लज्जमानाम्","m":"who was feeling abashed"},{"d":"यशस्विनीम्","m":"illustrious"},{"d":"अङ्केन","m":"arms"},{"d":"आदाय","m":"taking"},{"d":"विक्रान्तेन","m":"valiant"},{"d":"धनुष्मता","m":"archer"},{"d":"भ्रात्रा","m":"brother"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणेनसह","m":"with Lakshmana"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"अब्रवीत्सविमानस्थःपूजयन्सर्वावानरान् ।सुग्रीवं च महावीर्यंकाकुत्स्थसविभीषणम्","trans":"After duly honouring all the Vanaras, to Vibheeshana and highly courageous Sugriva, Kakuthsa spoke as follows.","words":[{"d":"सःकाकुत्स्थ:","m":"that Kakuthsa"},{"d":"विमानस्थः","m":"in the aerial car"},{"d":"सर्ववानरान्","m":"all Vanaras"},{"d":"सविभीषणम्","m":"and Vibheeshana"},{"d":"महावीर्यम्","m":"highly courageous"},{"d":"सुग्रीवं च","m":"Sugriva also"},{"d":"पूजयन्","m":"honoured"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"मित्रकार्यंकृतमिदंभवद्भिद्वानरर्षभाः ।अनुज्ञातामयासर्वेयथेष्टंप्रतिगच्छत","trans":"\"Bull among Vanaras! Since this work of the friend has been accomplished, you too have my permission to go where you will.\"","words":[{"d":"वानरर्षभाः","m":"bull among Vanaras"},{"d":"भवद्भिः","m":"you also"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"this"},{"d":"मित्रकार्यम्","m":"friend's work"},{"d":"कृतम्","m":"having done"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"मया","m":"my"},{"d":"अनुज्ञाताः","m":"per mission"},{"d":"यथेष्टम्","m":"as you will"},{"d":"प्रतिगच्छत","m":"can go"}]},{"v":15,"dev":"यत्तुकार्यंवयस्येनस्निग्धेन च हितेन च ।कृतंसुग्रीवतत्सर्वंभवताधर्मभीरुणा किष्किन्धांप्रतियाह्यावुस्वसैन्येनाभिसम्वृतः ।","trans":"All that has to be done by an affectionate friend in advanced age has been done, for the fear of unrighteousness. Now you may advance with your army to Kishkinda.","words":[{"d":"सुग्रीव","m":"Sugriva"},{"d":"स्निग्धेन","m":"affectionate"},{"d":"हितेन च","m":"What has to be done"},{"d":"वयस्येन","m":"advanced in age"},{"d":"यत् तु","m":"all that"},{"d":"कार्यम्","m":"work"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"सर्वम्","m":"everything"},{"d":"धर्मभीरुणा","m":"fear of unrighteousness"},{"d":"भवता","m":"by you"},{"d":"कृतम्","m":"done"},{"d":"आशु","m":"now"},{"d":"स्वसैन्येन","m":"with your own army"},{"d":"अभिसम्वृतः","m":"surrounding you"},{"d":"किष्किन्धाम्","m":"to Kishkinda"},{"d":"याहि","m":"can go"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"स्वराज्येवसलङ्कायांमयादत्तेविभीषण न त्वांधर्षयितुंशक्तास्सेन्द्राअपिदिवौकसः ।","trans":"\"Vibheeshana, I would like to see you living like Indra bestowed with your own kingdom in Lanka. It will not be possible for even gods to attack you.\"","words":[{"d":"विभीषण","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"लङ्कायाम्","m":"in Lanka"},{"d":"मया","m":"by me"},{"d":"दत्ते","m":"bestowed"},{"d":"स्वराज्ये","m":"own kingdom"},{"d":"वस","m":"living"},{"d":"नेन्द्राः","m":"Indra"},{"d":"दिवौकसःअपि","m":"gods in the heaven even"},{"d":"त्वाम्","m":"you"},{"d":"धर्षयितुम्","m":"will not be able to attack"},{"d":"न शक्ताः","m":"not possible"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"योध्यांप्रतियास्यामिराजधानींपितुर्मम अभ्यनुज्ञातुमिच्छामिसर्वानामन्त्रयामिवः ।","trans":"\"I shall proceed to my father's capital, Ayodhya. You may permit me. Be auspicious. I take leave of you.\"","words":[{"d":"ममपितुः","m":"my father's"},{"d":"राजधानीम्","m":"capital"},{"d":"अयोध्यांप्रति","m":"Lord of Ayodhya"},{"d":"यास्यामि","m":"to proceed for me"},{"d":"अभ्यनुज्ञातुम्","m":"you need to permit"},{"d":"इच्छामि","m":"I wish"},{"d":"वः","m":"be auspicious"},{"d":"सर्वान्","m":"all"},{"d":"अमंत्रयामि","m":"I take leave of"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"वमुक्तास्तुरामेणहरीन्द्राहरयस्तथा ऊचुःप्राञ्जलयस्सर्वेराक्षसश्चविभीषणः ।","trans":"After Rama had spoken that way Sugriva, Vibheeshana, monkeys and Rakshasas saluted Rama and said as follows.","words":[{"d":"रामेण","m":"by Rama"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"उक्ताः","m":"spoken"},{"d":"हरीन्द्राः","m":"Sugriva"},{"d":"तथा","m":"that way"},{"d":"हरयः","m":"monkeys"},{"d":"राक्षसः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"विभीषणश्च","m":"Vibheeshana's"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"प्राञ्जलयः","m":"saluting"},{"d":"ऊचुः","m":"said"}]},{"v":19,"dev":"अयोध्यांगन्तुमिच्छामःसर्वन्नयतुनोभवान् मुद्युक्ताविचरिष्यामोवनान्युपननानि च ।","trans":"We wish to proceed with you to Ayodhya, and many wishes to go with you and range the forests and groves without anxiety.","words":[{"d":"अयोध्याम्","m":"to Ayodhya"},{"d":"गन्तुम्","m":"proceed"},{"d":"इच्छामः","m":"wish"},{"d":"भवान्","m":"we"},{"d":"सर्वान्","m":"all"},{"d":"नः","m":"nay"},{"d":"नयतु","m":"to go"},{"d":"मुद्युक्ताः","m":"with you"},{"d":"वनानि","m":"forests"},{"d":"उपवनानि च","m":"groves"},{"d":"विचरिष्यामः","m":"will range without anxiety"}]},{"v":20,"dev":"दृष्टवात्वामभिषेकार्ध्रंकौसल्यामभिवाद्य च अचिरादगमिष्यामःस्वगृहान्नृपसत्तम ।","trans":"\"O Jewel among kings! We will see you being consecrated and see Kausalya, greet her and return back to our own house.\"","words":[{"d":"नृपसत्तम","m":"jewel among kings"},{"d":"अभिषेकार्द्रम्","m":"getting consecrated"},{"d":"त्वाम्","m":"you"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"कौसल्याम्","m":"Kausalya"},{"d":"अभिवाद्य च","m":"greeting"},{"d":"अचिरात्","m":"soon"},{"d":"स्वगृहान्","m":"own house"},{"d":"अगमिष्यामः","m":"will return"}]},{"v":21,"dev":"एवमुक्तस्सधर्मात्मावानरैस्सविभीषणैः अब्रवीद्वानरान्रामस्ससुग्रीवविभीषणान् ।","trans":"Vibheeshana and Vanaras had spoken in that way, Rama replied to Sugriva, Vibheeshana and Vanaras as follows.","words":[{"d":"सविभीषणैः","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"वानरैः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"उक्तः","m":"spoken"},{"d":"धर्मात्मा","m":"righteous"},{"d":"सःरामः","m":"he, Rama"},{"d":"ससुग्रीवविभीषणान्","m":"Sugriva and Vibheeshana"},{"d":"वानरान्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":22,"dev":"प्रिययतरंलब्दंयदहंससुहृज्जनः सर्वैर्भवद्भिःसहितःप्रीतिंलप्स्येपुरींगतः ।","trans":"\"If I with my dear and near and together with you go to Ayodhya, that will give more happiness with Sita coming and with all of you.\"","words":[{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"ससुहृज्जनः","m":"with my dear and near"},{"d":"सर्वैः","m":"all"},{"d":"भवद्भिः","m":"you also"},{"d":"सहितः","m":"together"},{"d":"पुरीम्","m":"Ayodhya"},{"d":"गतः","m":"go"},{"d":"प्रीतिम्","m":"happy"},{"d":"यत्","m":"that"},{"d":"लप्स्ये","m":"gain"},{"d":"प्रियात्","m":"dear Sita"},{"d":"प्रियतरम्","m":"very happy"},{"d":"लब्दम्","m":"give"}]},{"v":23,"dev":"क्षिप्रम् सुग्रीवविमानंवानरैस्सह त्वमप्यारोहसामात्योराक्षसेन्द्रविभीषण ।","trans":"Sugriva and the Vanaras, quickly ascended the aerial car. Vibheeshana, the king of Rakshasas and ministers all of them ascended.","words":[{"d":"सुग्रीव","m":"Sugriva"},{"d":"वानरैःसह","m":"with Vanaras"},{"d":"क्षिप्रम्","m":"quickly"},{"d":"विमानम्","m":"aerial car"},{"d":"आरोह","m":"ascended"},{"d":"राक्षसेन्द्रः","m":"Rakshasa king"},{"d":"विभीषण","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"सामात्यः","m":"ministers"},{"d":"त्वमपि","m":"all"},{"d":"आरोह","m":"ascended"}]},{"v":24,"dev":"ततः स पुष्पकंदिव्यंसुग्रीवस्सहवानरैः आरुरोहमुदायुक्तःसामात्यश्चविभीषणः ।","trans":"Then Sugriva with Vanaras happily joined the wonderful Pushpaka, Vibheeshana and his ministers also ascended.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"सःसुग्रीवः","m":"Sugriva"},{"d":"वानरैःसह","m":"with Vanaras"},{"d":"मुदा","m":"happy"},{"d":"युक्तः","m":"joined"},{"d":"दिव्यम्","m":"wonderful"},{"d":"पुष्पकम्","m":"Pushpaka"},{"d":"आरुरोह","m":"ascended"},{"d":"सामात्यः","m":"ministers"},{"d":"विभीषणश्च","m":"Vibheeshana"}]},{"v":25,"dev":"तेष्वारूढेषुसर्वेषुकौबेरंपरमासनम् राघवणाभ्यनुज्ञातमुत्पपातविहायसम् ।","trans":"All the Vanaras and others having got into Kubera's Pushpaka with Rama's permission, it flew into the sky.","words":[{"d":"तेषु","m":"those"},{"d":"सर्वेषु","m":"all"},{"d":"आरूढेषु","m":"having got in"},{"d":"कौबेरम्","m":"Kubera's"},{"d":"परमासनम्","m":"supreme seat"},{"d":"राघवेण","m":"by Raghava"},{"d":"अभ्यनुज्ञातम्","m":"with his permission"},{"d":"विहायसम्","m":"sky"},{"d":"उत्पपात","m":"flew"}]},{"v":26,"dev":"गतेनविमानेनहंसयुक्तेनभास्वता प्रहृष्टश्चप्रतीतश्चबभौरामःकुबेरवत् ।","trans":"Delighted and thrilled, Rama was flying in the sky in Pushpaka and with shining swans, he shone like Kubera.","words":[{"d":"प्रहृष्टश्च","m":"delighted"},{"d":"प्रतीतश्च","m":"thrilled"},{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"खगतेन","m":"in the sky"},{"d":"हंसयुक्तेन","m":"with pictures of swans"},{"d":"भास्वता","m":"shining"},{"d":"विमानेन","m":"by the aerial car"},{"d":"कुबेरवत्","m":"like Kubera"},{"d":"बभौ","m":"shone"}]}]}